<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.9.5">
<l>ceruvaḻi yāta maṉṉarkaḷ māḷat tērvalaṅ koṇṭavar cellum</l>
<l>aruvaḻi vāṉa matarpaṭak kaṇṭa vāṇmaiko lōvaṟi yēṉnāṉ</l>
<l>tirumoḻi yeṅkaḷ tēmalark kōtai cīrmaiyai niṉaintilai yantō</l>
<l>peruvaḻi nāvaṟ kaṉiyiṉu meḷiya ḷivaḷeṉap pēcukiṉ ṟāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[When you] conquered chariots so that the kings,</l>
<l rend="indent">[previously] undefeated in battle, died,</l>
<l>Was it manliness that [those kings] saw when [they] took to the road</l>
<l rend="indent">on the harrowing path to the heaven where they were going?</l>
<l>I don’t understand! You do not think of the reputation</l>
<l rend="indent">of [our] nectar[-laden] flower garland of heavenly speech.</l>
<l>Dear me! You speak of her as a woman lower than a rose-apple</l>
<l rend="indent">fallen on the main road.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
